1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,000
The fox demon Hu Sanlang — had not gone far.

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:12,000
As she left the banquet — he stepped out from behind a tree.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:17,000
My Lady — wait.

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:23,000
I forgot one thing.

5
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:29,000
What thing?

6
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:36,000
Three silver needles between his fingers — tips glowing blue. Poisoned.

7
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:43,000
The formula is real — but its final ingredient, only one person in this kingdom has.

8
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:46,000
Who?

9
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:51,000
The Empress Dowager.

10
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:58,000
Qingxin Pill needs Thousand-Year Cold Iron — hidden in her chambers.

11
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:04,000
So this formula — is no formula at all?

12
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:10,000
At least you know what you need. How to get it — that is yours.

13
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:15,000
What do you really want?

14
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:22,000
I want — you to owe me a favor.

15
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:30,000
Kill Zhao Tieyi for me — and I am yours from then on.

16
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:36,000
You can't even beat me — what use are you to me?

17
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:44,000
I can't beat you — but I steal, I listen, I lay traps. You don't.

18
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:50,000
Fine — Zhao Tieyi, after I return from the borderlands.

19
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:54,000
My thanks, my Lady!

20
00:01:54,000 --> 00:02:01,000
One more thing.

21
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:09,000
The Empress has brought a Fifth-Rank Demon Master into the palace — for you alone.

22
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:13,000
I know.

23
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:19,000
The fox demon — dissolved into red smoke.

24
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:24,000
My lady — are you all right?

25
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:32,000
How strong must one become — to be free of every threat?

26
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:38,000
My lady is already very strong.

27
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:43,000
Not enough. Far from enough.

28
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:50,000
Three months — they will be here in three months at most.

29
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:58,000
Three months — from Silver Rank to Gold Rank, and beyond.

30
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:04,000
The fastest way — kill demons. Refine more demonic blood.

31
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:10,000
Tomorrow morning — I will see the Emperor.

32
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:14,000
My lady wishes to see — His Majesty?

33
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:20,000
Yes. The demon kings of the border won't wait. Neither will I.

34
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:28,000
She clenched her fist — dark-gold patterns emerged on her arm, gleaming cold in the moonlight.

35
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:35,000
This blade — is ready to be drawn.
